726795f-a.title: Queens: Grand Central Parkwa - Parsons Boulevard
726795f-a.text:
Grand Central Parkway, west from Parsons Boulevard, showing the highway under construction. On the left is an unpaved street, formerly known as Lott Lane.
March 25, 1932
P. L. Sperr
726795f-a.folder: Grand Central Parkwa & Parsons Boulevard, Queens, NY

727676f-a.text:
Parsons Boulevard (foreground), at the N.W. corer of Grand Central Parkway, showing an old homestead. The house and a 50-acre farm was owned by J. Lott in 1873. Phoebe Ely owned the property in 1909. View 2 shows Grand Central Parkway under construction.
Lott Lane formerly ran here.
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS  View 1: March 27, 1927
View 2: March 25, 1932
